    "One's eyes never wandered far as the teachers were always the epitome of expertise.",
    "However, Henry, as truly economic, made it clear that he expected one not to participate in the abundance that surrounded them until all the classes were over and done with.",
    "Similarly, District Judge Thomas J. Curran remarked:",
    "Frankly, I did not expect such a concentrated agenda.",
    "I don't believe I have ever attended a seminar that involved such intensive study and discussion."
